folder: Mount Eden Avenue & Monroe Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Mount Eden Avenue - Monroe Avenue
text:
301-305 Mt. Eden Ave., at the N.E. corner of Monroe Ave., showing the Annette Court. The three frame dwellings, on the left, bear numbers 1650 to 1654 Monroe Ave.

About 1929.
